---
title: "transferForSwap (FeeAggregator)"
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_check_empty: check assetAmounts.length
    q_check_empty --> q_error_empty: length == 0
    q_error_empty --> [*]: revert EmptyList
    q_check_empty --> q_loop: length > 0
    q_loop --> q_check_allowlist: for each assetAmount
    q_check_allowlist --> q_error_asset: !allowlisted(asset)
    q_error_asset --> [*]: revert AssetNotAllowlisted
    q_check_allowlist --> q_transfer: allowlisted(asset)
    q_transfer --> q_loop: _transferAsset(to, asset, amount)
    q_loop --> [*]: all assets transferred

    note right of q_check_allowlist
        INV-001: Only allowlisted assets can be transferred out
        INV-002: Caller must have SWAPPER_ROLE
        INV-003: Contract must not be paused
    end note
